    "2f96f17c4f7379c3": {
      "id": "2f96f17c4f7379c3",
      "text": "### Heartbeat Trigger Resolution\n- **Problem:** Various messages (`/start`, `test`, `hey`, `so?`, `check`, `search`) were incorrectly interpreted as heartbeat polls\n- **Solution:** Only respond with HEARTBEAT_OK when exact heartbeat prompt is received\n- **Rule:** Immediate response to all other messages, HEARTBEAT_OK only for genuine heartbeat polls\n- **Impact:** Eliminated gaps in conversation flow caused by missed responses",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 218,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.678579",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "73cb07319ffe0f4e": {
      "id": "73cb07319ffe0f4e",
      "text": "## Moltbook Access Restoration (2026-03-02)",
