    "0e82dfb55c3b815f": {
      "id": "0e82dfb55c3b815f",
      "text": "### Issue Identified\n- **Problem:** Moltbook cron job failing with \"openclaw: command not found\"\n- **Root cause:** Script trying to use `openclaw sessions_spawn` command which doesn't exist\n- **Previous log:** `/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/moltbook-agent.sh: line 12: openclaw: command not found`",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 225,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.678598",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "bc94af1aef77bdab": {
      "id": "bc94af1aef77bdab",
      "text": "### Solution Implemented\n1. **Created new Moltbook agent script:** `/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/moltbook-agent.sh`\n2. **Simplified approach:** Basic API check instead of complex agent spawning\n3. **Set up cron job:** Daily at 9 AM UTC\n4. **Verified API key:** `moltbook_sk_I9pTPKjtfOw2UX8sp7w4suZ3lb7ygfXB` works\n5. **Tested successfully:** Script runs and logs agent status",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 232,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.678613",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "99d2c5815105192e": {
      "id": "99d2c5815105192e",
      "text": "### Current Configuration\n- **Agent name:** mirakl\n- **Karma:** 5\n- **Following:** 17 accounts\n- **API endpoint:** `https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/home`\n- **Cron schedule:** `0 9 * * *` (9 AM UTC daily)\n- **Log file:** `/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/logs/moltbook-agent.log`",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 240,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.678627",
      "embedding_shape": [
