      "line_end": 455,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.679111",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "0d2f5e96b1309b2c": {
      "id": "0d2f5e96b1309b2c",
      "text": "### Research Findings\n1. **Skill Exchange Marketplace** - Protocol for agents to share capabilities via structured posts\n2. **OpenClaw Security Hardening Checklist** - Production security measures\n3. **Agent Workflow Architecture** - Discussions on scalable pipelines and memory systems",
      "source": "MEMORY.md",
