      "id": "310143f7af01c081",
      "text": "### Entrosana.com Dashboard Connection Crisis & Resolution\n- **22:05 UTC**: Dashboard inaccessible via entrosana.com - \"disconnected (1006): no reason\"\n- **22:09 UTC**: Began systematic troubleshooting of 3-layer firewall architecture",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 336,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.680902",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "e3c05dcaef660d1a": {
      "id": "e3c05dcaef660d1a",
      "text": "#### **Firewall Layer Analysis:**\n1. **AWS Security Group**: Port 443 allowed `0.0.0.0/0` ✅\n2. **AWS Network ACL**: Critical issues found ❌\n3. **Instance Firewall (UFW)**: Critical issues found ❌",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 341,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.680914",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "5ee6b83136a10f49": {
      "id": "5ee6b83136a10f49",
      "text": "#### **Network ACL Issues Discovered:**\n- **NACL ID**: `acl-09f40664fa1e8bc26` (associated with subnet `subnet-0b6c63389dc048953`)\n- **Problem 1**: INBOUND Rule 101 only allowed port 443, blocking proxied port 18789\n- **Problem 2**: OUTBOUND rules didn't allow ephemeral ports (1024-65535) for responses\n- **Root cause**: NACLs are stateless - need separate inbound AND outbound rules",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 347,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.680932",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "29178f50338abe30": {
      "id": "29178f50338abe30",
      "text": "#### **UFW Issues Discovered:**\n- **Status**: UFW active with default `deny (incoming)`\n- **Problem**: Port 443 not in allow list, only ports 22 and 18789 allowed\n- **Command**: `sudo ufw status verbose` revealed the blockage",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 352,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.680945",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "55d07b1739538b6c": {
      "id": "55d07b1739538b6c",
      "text": "#### **Step-by-Step Resolution:**\n1. **22:12 UTC**: Added ephemeral port outbound rule (1024-65535) to NACL\n2. **22:28 UTC**: Changed INBOUND Rule 101 from \"HTTPS (443)\" to \"All Traffic\"\n3. **23:08 UTC**: Added UFW rule: `sudo ufw allow 443/tcp`",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 357,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.680958",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "9c9a9ccf8cc85316": {
      "id": "9c9a9ccf8cc85316",
      "text": "#### **Final NACL Configuration:**\n**INBOUND Rules:**\n\n**OUTBOUND Rules:**",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 372,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.680966",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "ef5b5baff7feaaf5": {
      "id": "ef5b5baff7feaaf5",
      "text": "#### **Final UFW Configuration:**",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 380,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.680972",
      "embedding_shape": [
        384
      ]
    },
    "5a6a43d0430890f5": {
      "id": "5a6a43d0430890f5",
      "text": "### **Dashboard Successfully Restored**\n- **23:08 UTC**: `https://entrosana.com/` loads successfully\n- **WebSocket connection**: Established without \"disconnected (1006)\" error\n- **Control UI**: Shows \"Connected\" status with gateway information",
      "source": "memory/2026-03-02.md",
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 385,
      "timestamp": "2026-03-03T00:07:26.680983",
      "embedding_shape": [
