      "text": "### **Technical Notes:**\n- **Model loading**: First-time download warning about unauthenticated HF Hub requests (can set HF_TOKEN for higher limits)\n- **E5 requirement**: Must prefix texts with \"query: \" or \"passage: \" (handled automatically)\n- **Normalization**: Embeddings are L2-normalized for cosine similarity\n- **CPU efficiency**: Works well without GPU acceleration",
